{n}The shamans words become quieter and quieter.{/n} "We be {g|Lamashtu}Lamashtu's{/g} sons... watering... seed-sowing... readying... for the season… of Bloom... All together... boom... boom... boom..."
{n}The shaman emits a long wheeze and freezes, looking straight into your eyes. His dull eyes are lit by an evil flicker.{/n}
"The season of Bloom has begun. You no stop us."
